---
title: Honey-Garlic Double Chicken with Brussels Sprouts and Sweet Potato Mash
description: Sometimes all you need is a simple sauce to take your dinner to the next level! Tonight's easy honey-garlic sauce makes this chicken dish truly shine. We've paired it with garlicky Brussels sprouts and fluffy sweet potato mash for a match made in heaven!
